  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SUPERVERSE</strong> is a fast-paced, action-packed space shooter that launches you into an ancient network of interconnected universes. Your mission: travel back through space-time and prevent the extinction of humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rely solely on your instincts, reflexes, speed, devastating weapons, and protective shield as you navigate hostile environments filled with enemy ships, asteroids, explosions, and volatile cosmic particles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056170/extras/2f31c2b42ec40804f944627b2cb50088.poster.avif?t=1765506266\" width=620 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056170/extras/2f31c2b42ec40804f944627b2cb50088.webm?t=1765506266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056170/extras/2f31c2b42ec40804f944627b2cb50088.mp4?t=1765506266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In SUPERVERSE you will:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through wormholes and explore new, mysterious worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the game from the perspective of an Artificial Intelligence</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle advanced AI-controlled enemy ships and machines</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly your favorite spaceship and master its unique abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an immersive 3D visual and audio experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play cooperatively with friends—locally or online—or take on the universe solo </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>SUPERVERSE can be played on <strong>Windows</strong> and <strong>Linux</strong>¹.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SUPERVERSE</strong> is a fast-paced, action-packed space shooter that launches you into an ancient network of interconnected universes. Your mission: travel back through space-time and prevent the extinction of humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rely solely on your instincts, reflexes, speed, devastating weapons, and protective shield as you navigate hostile environments filled with enemy ships, asteroids, explosions, and volatile cosmic particles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056170/extras/2f31c2b42ec40804f944627b2cb50088.poster.avif?t=1765506266\" width=620 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056170/extras/2f31c2b42ec40804f944627b2cb50088.webm?t=1765506266\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056170/extras/2f31c2b42ec40804f944627b2cb50088.mp4?t=1765506266\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In SUPERVERSE you will:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through wormholes and explore new, mysterious worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the game from the perspective of an Artificial Intelligence</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle advanced AI-controlled enemy ships and machines</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fly your favorite spaceship and master its unique abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an immersive 3D visual and audio experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play cooperatively with friends—locally or online—or take on the universe solo </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>SUPERVERSE can be played on <strong>Windows</strong> and <strong>Linux</strong>¹.</i></p>",
